Canada computers Mississauga is ok if you speak English but I find I can only gethalf decent service if I speak Cantonese in markham especially the pacific mall location. Tiger direct Canada is pretty good too though they have a habit of splitting my orders two pieces at a time which annoys me. My favorite is Ncix if I can make the trip to markham.

Canada Computers near College/Spadina is probably the best place for computer hardware. In the area you'll also find a lot of shops focused on electronics and other goodies, so if you're into that it's a fun stroll.
